### Test Email Notifications for Order Status Updates
# This file can be used to test all email notification functionality

### 1. Update payment status to COMPLETED (should trigger payment confirmation email)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/orders/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

{
  "paymentStatus": "COMPLETED"
}

### 2. Update payment status to FAILED (should trigger payment failure email)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/orders/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

{
  "paymentStatus": "FAILED"
}

### 3. Update order status to SHIPPED (should trigger shipping notification email)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/orders/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

{
  "status": "SHIPPED",
  "shippingCarrier": "Giao Hàng Nhanh",
  "trackingNumber": "GHN123456789"
}

### 4. Update order status to DELIVERED (should trigger completion thank you email)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/orders/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

{
  "status": "DELIVERED"
}

### 5. Test multiple updates at once
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/orders/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

{
  "status": "SHIPPED",
  "paymentStatus": "COMPLETED",
  "shippingCarrier": "Viettel Post",
  "trackingNumber": "VTP987654321",
  "notes": "Đơn hàng đã được xử lý và giao cho đơn vị vận chuyển"
}